name: FLAME
description: FLAME is a memecoin project designed to inspire creativity and bring fun into the world of blockchain. With its distinctive dragon theme, FLAME captures the imagination of its community, creating a unique blend of entertainment and decentralized finance. The project aims to engage a growing audience of crypto enthusiasts by fostering a vibrant community and introducing innovative ways to participate in the ecosystem. By merging playful branding with blockchain technology, FLAME seeks to provide both an enjoyable experience and potential opportunities for its users.
